reviewText: I actually wanted to give this 3 stars cos my husband found  it creepy / hilarious. The babies "sing" their little moving mouths ala' Conan O'Brien. So some  of the babies  look pretty creepy, at times leaving  me and my husband to say aloud in unison, " Oh my God!" Yet, my daughter SUPER loves it! She watched both videos back to back and clapped, danced and was mesmerized by the creepy baby mouth effects but it's the best thing since booby milk for her!
